    <item>
      <title>智利打击犯罪者成为左翼总统候选人的热门人选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/chile-crime-fighter-emerges-as-left-wing-s-presidential-favorite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项早期民意调查显示，智利内政部长卡罗莱纳·托哈是今年总统大选中潜在中左翼候选人中最受欢迎的人选，但未来几个月联盟将推出哪位候选人的争论愈演愈烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/chile-crime-fighter-emerges-as-left-wing-s-presidential-favorite</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西民众对经济持悲观态度，卢拉不满程度再创新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/lula-disapproval-hits-new-high-with-brazilians-pessimistic-about-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们对巴西左翼总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦的经济管理方式越来越不满，12 月份他对这位总统的不满达到了其任期内的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/lula-disapproval-hits-new-high-with-brazilians-pessimistic-about-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷人对米莱伊经济越来越乐观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/argentines-are-increasingly-positive-about-the-milei-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷人对该国陷入困境的经济的未来变得更加乐观，这一转变将在今年晚些时候的中期选举之前鼓舞主张紧缩政策的总统哈维尔·米莱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/argentines-are-increasingly-positive-about-the-milei-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥民众谴责犯罪和腐败，谢恩鲍姆支持率下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/sheinbaum-s-support-slips-as-mexicans-decry-crime-and-corruption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项最新民意调查显示，由于选民强烈要求墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·希因鲍姆采取更强有力的打击犯罪和腐败的行动，其支持率在其执政约 100 天后下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/sheinbaum-s-support-slips-as-mexicans-decry-crime-and-corruption</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
